{"type":"answer","id":115553,"parentType":"question","parentId":14165,"uid":21532,"contents":"北京大学马克思主义学会已经非法了 :) 不知道你要的是<i>这个</i>马克思主义呢，还是<i>那个</i>马克思主义呢？<br>\n<br>\n还是那句话，<b>斯大林已经败坏了马克思主义的名声，布尔什维克又进一步<a href=\"http://culture.ifeng.com/sixiang/detail_2014_02/12/33745287_1.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">败坏了整个左派的名声</a></b>。必须要彻底清算切割。总是在官僚专制的问题上遮遮掩掩，这样是不行的。<br>\n<br>\n大大方方地搞修正主义。社民拎得清，所以社民就没怎么被喷。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/TyDFzka.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TyDFzka.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/TyDFzka.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-27","agreeCount":9,"discussionCount":5}